---
// src/components/FAQ.astro
---

<section id="faq" class="py-24 bg-base-100 reveal">
  <div class="max-w-[85rem] px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 mx-auto">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center mb-10 lg:mb-14">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-black text-primary sm:text-4xl uppercase tracking-tight">
        Często Zadawane <span class="text-primary">Pytania</span>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <div class="hs-accordion-group">
        
        <div class="hs-accordion active bg-base-100 border border-transparent rounded-2xl p-6 mb-4 transition-all duration-300 hs-accordion-active:bg-base-100 hs-accordion-active:border-base-300" id="hs-basic-heading-one">
          <button class="hs-accordion-toggle group inline-flex items-center gap-x-3 w-full font-heading font-bold text-start text-base-content hover:text-primary focus:outline-none transition" 
                  aria-expanded="true"
                  aria-controls="hs-basic-collapse-one"
                  aria-label="What is the work schedule in your company">
            <svg class="hs-accordion-active:hidden block size-5 text-base-content/70 group-hover:text-primary" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="M12 5v14"/></svg>
            <svg class="hs-accordion-active:block hidden size-5 text-primary" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14"/></svg>
            Jaki jest grafik pracy w Waszej firmie?
          </button>
          <div id="hs-basic-collapse-one" class="hs-accordion-content w-full overflow-hidden transition-[height] duration-300" role="region" aria-labelledby="hs-basic-heading-one">
            <p class="text-base-content/70 mt-4 leading-relaxed font-sans">
              Oferujemy kilka grafików pracy do wyboru: 4 tygodnie pracy / 1 tydzień urlopu, 5/1, 6/2, 8/4, lub weekendy w domu. Możliwe indywidualne ustalenia grafiku.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hs-accordion bg-base-100 border border-transparent rounded-2xl p-6 mb-4 transition-all duration-300 hs-accordion-active:bg-base-100 hs-accordion-active:border-base-300" id="hs-basic-heading-two">
          <button class="hs-accordion-toggle group inline-flex items-center gap-x-3 w-full font-heading font-bold text-start text-base-content hover:text-primary focus:outline-none transition" 
                  aria-expanded="false"
                  aria-controls="hs-basic-collapse-two"
                  aria-label="What truck models and trailers do you use">
            <svg class="hs-accordion-active:hidden block size-5 text-base-content/70 group-hover:text-primary" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="M12 5v14"/></svg>
            <svg class="hs-accordion-active:block hidden size-5 text-primary" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14"/></svg>
            Jakie modele ciężarówek i naczep używamy?
          </button>
          <div id="hs-basic-collapse-two" class="hs-accordion-content hidden w-full overflow-hidden transition-[height] duration-300" role="region" aria-labelledby="hs-basic-heading-two">
            <p class="text-base-content/70 mt-4 leading-relaxed font-sans">
              Używamy najnowszych modeli ciężarówek spełniających normy środowiskowe Euro 6 - marki SCANIA i VOLVO. Naczepy to głównie firankowe.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hs-accordion bg-base-100 border border-transparent rounded-2xl p-6 mb-4 transition-all duration-300 hs-accordion-active:bg-base-100 hs-accordion-active:border-base-300" id="hs-basic-heading-three">
          <button class="hs-accordion-toggle group inline-flex items-center gap-x-3 w-full font-heading font-bold text-start text-base-content hover:text-primary focus:outline-none transition" 
                  aria-expanded="false"
                  aria-controls="hs-basic-collapse-three"
                  aria-label="What documents are required for employment">
            <svg class="hs-accordion-active:hidden block size-5 text-base-content/70 group-hover:text-primary" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="M12 5v14"/></svg>
            <svg class="hs-accordion-active:block hidden size-5 text-primary" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14"/></svg>
            Jakie dokumenty są wymagane do zatrudnienia?
          </button>
          <div id="hs-basic-collapse-three" class="hs-accordion-content hidden w-full overflow-hidden transition-[height] duration-300" role="region" aria-labelledby="hs-basic-heading-three">
            <p class="text-base-content/70 mt-4 leading-relaxed font-sans">
              Będziesz potrzebować: paszport, prawo jazdy C+E, Kod 95, kartę kierowcy, wizę lub kartę pobytu (Karta Pobytu).
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hs-accordion bg-base-100 border border-transparent rounded-2xl p-6 mb-4 transition-all duration-300 hs-accordion-active:bg-base-100 hs-accordion-active:border-base-300" id="hs-basic-heading-four">
          <button class="hs-accordion-toggle group inline-flex items-center gap-x-3 w-full font-heading font-bold text-start text-base-content hover:text-primary focus:outline-none transition" 
                  aria-expanded="false"
                  aria-controls="hs-basic-collapse-four"
                  aria-label="How is the work with dispatchers organized">
            <svg class="hs-accordion-active:hidden block size-5 text-base-content/70 group-hover:text-primary" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="M12 5v14"/></svg>
            <svg class="hs-accordion-active:block hidden size-5 text-primary" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14"/></svg>
            Jak zorganizowana jest praca z dyspozytorami?
          </button>
          <div id="hs-basic-collapse-four" class="hs-accordion-content hidden w-full overflow-hidden transition-[height] duration-300" role="region" aria-labelledby="hs-basic-heading-four">
            <p class="text-base-content/70 mt-4 leading-relaxed font-sans">
              Nasi dyspozytorzy mówią po rosyjsku, polsku i angielsku i zapewniają wsparcie 24/7. Możesz się z nimi skontaktować w każdej chwili, aby uzyskać pomoc w każdej sprawie.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hs-accordion bg-base-100 border border-transparent rounded-2xl p-6 mb-4 transition-all duration-300 hs-accordion-active:bg-base-100 hs-accordion-active:border-base-300" id="hs-basic-heading-five">
          <button class="hs-accordion-toggle group inline-flex items-center gap-x-3 w-full font-heading font-bold text-start text-base-content hover:text-primary focus:outline-none transition" 
                  aria-expanded="false"
                  aria-controls="hs-basic-collapse-five"
                  aria-label="What routes are used for transportation">
            <svg class="hs-accordion-active:hidden block size-5 text-base-content/70 group-hover:text-primary" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="M12 5v14"/></svg>
            <svg class="hs-accordion-active:block hidden size-5 text-primary" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14"/></svg>
            W jakich krajach działamy?
          </button>
          <div id="hs-basic-collapse-five" class="hs-accordion-content hidden w-full overflow-hidden transition-[height] duration-300" role="region" aria-labelledby="hs-basic-heading-five">
            <p class="text-base-content/70 mt-4 leading-relaxed font-sans mb-3">
              Działamy w całej Unii Europejskiej z naciskiem na <span class="font-bold text-primary">Benelux</span> (Belgia, Holandia, Luksemburg), <span class="font-bold text-primary">Niemcy</span> i <span class="font-bold text-primary">Francję</span>. Dodatkowo obsługujemy trasy do Szwajcarii, Włoch, Hiszpanii i Portugalii.
            </p>
            <p class="text-base-content/60 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans">
              Wszystkie trasy są dobrze ugruntowane ze stałymi punktami załadunku, wygodnymi miejscami wypoczynku i sprawdzonymi partnerstwami, które zapewniają stabilną pracę i przewidywalne grafiki.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hs-accordion bg-base-100 border border-transparent rounded-2xl p-6 transition-all duration-300 hs-accordion-active:bg-base-100 hs-accordion-active:border-base-300" id="hs-basic-heading-six">
          <button class="hs-accordion-toggle group inline-flex items-center gap-x-3 w-full font-heading font-bold text-start text-base-content hover:text-primary focus:outline-none transition" 
                  aria-expanded="false"
                  aria-controls="hs-basic-collapse-six"
                  aria-label="Do I need to do pallet exchanges or night driving">
            <svg class="hs-accordion-active:hidden block size-5 text-base-content/70 group-hover:text-primary" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="M12 5v14"/></svg>
            <svg class="hs-accordion-active:block hidden size-5 text-primary" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14"/></svg>
            Czy muszę wymieniać palety lub jeździć nocą?
          </button>
          <div id="hs-basic-collapse-six" class="hs-accordion-content hidden w-full overflow-hidden transition-[height] duration-300" role="region" aria-labelledby="hs-basic-heading-six">
            <p class="text-base-content/70 mt-4 leading-relaxed font-sans">
              <span class="font-bold text-primary">Nie!</span> W Dartrans priorytetem jest komfort i bezpieczeństwo kierowcy. <span class="font-bold">NIE</span> będziesz musiał wymieniać palet, przestawiać naczep ani jeździć nocą. Nasze trasy są zaprojektowane tak, aby były proste i bezstresowe, pozwalając Ci skupić się na bezpiecznej jeździe i utrzymaniu zdrowej równowagi między życiem zawodowym a prywatnym.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>